  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Purpose of the study is to assess the utility of PSD Veritas as a staple line reinforcement
      to minimize the risk of leakage during or after colo-rectal surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Study is designed as a prospective enrollment of patients undergoing open or laparoscopic
      colorectal surgery requiring the creation of an anastomosis. Patients who are scheduled for
      elective resection of the left, anterior and low anterior colon can be enrolled in the study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
